Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要 不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西一定要用我的法術毀掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.57,0:01:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠志郎先生離開有馬神社已經好幾天了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.24,0:01:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親為了處理連續發生的少女命案而煩惱著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們三姊妹也只能乖乖的待在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.12,0:01:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這樣所以蠻寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\c&HC83232&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1\fad(300,0)}第二夜 覺醒之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說昨天晚上又有一位女孩子被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這加起來是第三位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人不知是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:01:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可怕吧 柚鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 有在聽我說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.09,0:02:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自從悠志郎先生不在以後 妳就變得很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遲到了 遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開 昨天作了怪夢 害我睡過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月還是老樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠志郎先生不在以後對她好像沒影響
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以為沒有吵架的對象後她會無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反倒是柚鈴妳覺得寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為已經約定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:02:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 沒辦法那麼快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心 事情一辦完就會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠志郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我回來前請幫我保管這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會很小心保管的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,0:03:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和妳約定了 一定會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠志郎先生能快點回來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前都沒注意到火車的汽笛聲 就像這口琴聲一樣悲愁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 愛一個人是如此心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠志郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得柚鈴很寂寞 所以來陪妳一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是妳不是做了惡夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被拆穿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳剛剛在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 只是準備要睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候我們常常這樣子睡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月是做了惡夢才會來這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果被知道我這時還在柚鈴這邊 我會被媽媽罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且最近常常做很可怕的惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 今天是來安慰柚鈴的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚鈴 悠志郎不在以後妳好像很沒精神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:05:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠志郎的口琴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為悠志郎回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳喜歡那傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 趕快說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 美月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實妳喜歡他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好癢 這個 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大 比我還大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 癢死妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 摸 摸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命 摸 摸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 這個 還不從實招來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求饒吧 求饒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳很喜歡他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美 美月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美 美月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪呢 美月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們倆個要鬧到何時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.07,0:07:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們以為幾點了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼丟臉的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月 妳給我回去自己的房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚鈴也快點睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時候快到了 再不快點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個妖魅 再過不久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有馬小姐 有信來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個和尚真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒看過和尚會在神社外面徘徊的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳看 就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.53,0:08:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近怪事變多了 請多注意一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是悠志郎先生寫來的信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那上面有寫何時回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面好像沒寫何時回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親的情況比想像中輕微 也許不久就會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那請大家多多保重身體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就可以放心準備祭典了 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:09:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 沒錯 萬事能這樣就最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是我講的笑話不好笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠志郎也不用那麼快回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是不是太閒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說來 今天看到一個奇怪的和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是修行僧的樣子 感覺得噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修行僧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該不會這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 老師在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過是貧血 不用到保健室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 要是有人的話就讓他吃我的鐵拳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了 到底是什麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 謝 悠 悠志郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要摸 我可以自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:10:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才不像沒問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我背著妳走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以自己一個人走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這只是小事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 我來背妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來背妳上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠志郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這聲音是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠志郎先生 歡迎你回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚鈴 讓妳久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 美月 什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請妳快點叫媽媽過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 美月怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是平常的貧血而已 只要睡一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠志郎先生 真是辛苦你了 請你好好的休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣麻煩了一陣子呢 是嗎 發生了這樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠志郎先生回來後 有馬家裡又展現了難得的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚鈴也覺得很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這只是有馬家的災難開始的前兆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像火一樣熱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救我 很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有遵守約定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 讓我覺得很放心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.26,0:14:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 這麼晚了要到哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很想念妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠志郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要住手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠志郎先生好過份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月居然說出這麼平常的話 是不是還在發燒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那麼誠懇的道謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼精神就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又變回平常的美月 我就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不理你了 悠志郎這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快點會趕不上吃早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 還這麼有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是年輕的女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這已經是第六個了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:15:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是年輕的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被害者的年齡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20幾歲前後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 不是我認識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還會再有犧牲者的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 那和尚很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼這樣就可以結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚鈴和美月說要讓你好好吃一頓 現正在一起下廚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是特別呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 連美月也一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是雙葉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有位朋友不見了 你們有看到我以外的女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒有看到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是從何時不見的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.76,0:16:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從昨天開始 除了這附近以外我全找過了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是都沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為最近的事件在擔心她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且下午在那事件現場的附近有位怪怪的修行僧說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「還會有犧牲者出現」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修行僧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那人或會知道這些連續事件的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許那人就是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 也許是想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在如果妳也失蹤了可是很糟糕的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下我來幫妳查查神社的四周
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月會來幫忙做菜真是難得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了要報答悠志郎那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連美月的份都要一起用心去做了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有學過 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,割到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都流血了 給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只被割到一下 沒流那麼多血啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是沒看到女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 一個人在這地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好怕 好怕 覺得自己越來越不像自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.22,0:18:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後今天又做了可怕的惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛又 剛剛又
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:18:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰都會有心煩的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎麼說妳也是有馬神社的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有事的話 神也會保佑妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼的不安感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到我的身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 像這樣過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.15,0:19:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到我身邊來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠志郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:19:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月 美月不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請悠志郎先生幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一定是那個人用了神威的法術
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神威
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 那人想殺了美月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺 殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詳細的事情現在不方便說明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在能從神威的手中保護美月 就只有悠志郎先生了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你保護美月 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉桐 請妳抬起頭來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 不管如何先找美月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手 要搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼醒了嗎 是誰 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾是為了除去世上墮落之神的術者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管你是啥 居然對不認識的女子這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算哪門子的東西 笑死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳也該發覺了才是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在妳身體內的魔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然妳要到何時才覺醒我是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但以我的力量是絕對不會讓妳覺醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這機會只有現在了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種地方還有貼符
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.16,0:22:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.30,0:22:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.04,0:22:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠志郎救我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.64,0:22:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開美月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救我悠志郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 不要阻礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你也是神威一族就乖乖的看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.99,0:22:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 這和神威沒有關係 我也不知道這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.60,0:22:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但想要美月性命的人我都不會輕饒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何我會有這種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.56,0:23:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.83,0:23:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.57,0:23:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.37,0:23:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是救了那女孩 將來你會後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.38,0:23:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠志郎你不會後悔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.58,0:23:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.32,0:23:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.19,0:23:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.73,0:23:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託 抱我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.53,0:23:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去我很怕不知道會變成什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.33,0:24:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不抓緊誰的話就好像要崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.34,0:24:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.34,0:24:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣不像是美月啊 請冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.82,0:24:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請好好的看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.29,0:24:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.56,0:24:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託 悠志郎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.57,0:24:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.64,0:24:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我的胸部比較小 有點害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.65,0:24:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.32,0:24:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還會越來越大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.05,0:24:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.73,0:25:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把手放進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.66,0:25:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣會漏出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.67,0:25:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這樣弄 好丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.87,0:25:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就自己來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.74,0:25:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要 要怎樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.22,0:25:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像要融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.76,0:25:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經
